            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/03/11/rand-paul-shockwaves-continue-now-the-democrats-are-at-war/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Rand Paul Filibuster Shockwaves Continue&#8230;Now the Democrats are at War"><span>6</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/aumf/" rel="tag">AUMF</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/barbara-lee/" rel="tag">Barbara Lee</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/cia/" rel="tag">CIA</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/congress/" rel="tag">Congress</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/drones/" rel="tag">drones</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/john-brennan/" rel="tag">John Brennan</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/john-conyers/" rel="tag">John Conyers</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/targeted-killings/" rel="tag">Targeted Killings</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/03/11/rand-paul-shockwaves-continue-now-the-democrats-are-at-war/#comments">6</a> 
