            <footer class="post-footer">
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/03/11/its-time-to-repeal-the-aumf/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on It&#8217;s Time to Repeal the AUMF"><span>1</span> Comment</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/al-qaeda/" rel="tag">Al Qaeda</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/associates-of-associates/" rel="tag">Associates of Associates</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/authorization-for-use-of-military-force/" rel="tag">Authorization for Use of Military Force</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/drones/" rel="tag">drones</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/jeh-johnson/" rel="tag">Jeh Johnson</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/liberty/" rel="tag">Liberty</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/war-on-terror/" rel="tag">war on terror</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/03/11/its-time-to-repeal-the-aumf/#comments">2</a> 
